Hi :) i'm here with another version of my favorite deck since 2010 NOW for Master duel. This singular version is optimized to play against Maxx C and Ash Blossom. (2 Gamma's. 2 Called and 3 Ash) and maintaining the light attribute spots for Chaos Ruler.

Gamma works well even playing 1st due to Crimson Resonator and Inca package (Dawnwalker and Duskwalker) being a hand trigger effect. If your opp triggers maxx c to crimson resonator and you gamma it you will gain a free chaos ruler + light monsters on grave as extenders.

&nbsp;

A particular add on this deck was Red familiar. I used to play Witch of black forest, she's good, but only works on field. Red familiar can work as a discard, you can tribute it from field sometimes to get a synchro used from grave and the main reason: from grave you can banish it and module your synchro levels to start your plays from bottom again. One of this deck issues was the fact that it will have follow up from grave, but if you don't draw a non-tuner top deck you can't use de rest of your lvl 6's from extra deck properly.

&nbsp;

that's it. hope you guys enjoy :)

