LARGE HAND LOOP 3 COMBO: Open with revealer and atlantean dragoon. Activate revealers effect to discard dragoon and special summon geomancer. Dragoons was sent to the graveyard to activate a water monsters ability so add a sea serpent monster to hand, add neptabyss, atlantean prince to your hand. Activate geomancer to discard a card and declare an attribute, discard neptabyss. Neptabyss GY effect triggers to special summon dragoons back onto the field. XYZ summon Bahamut shark using Revealer &amp; Dragoons. Activate Bahamut Shark's ability to detach dragoons to special summon toadally awesome. Dragoons was sent to the graveyard again, so search Lappis Dragon. Activate lappis dragon to special summon from your hand onto the field. Link summon using Lappis Dragon and Bahamut shark for Marincess coral anemone, activate Anemone's ability to special summon Neptabyss from your graveyard, activate Neptabyss effect to send dragoons to graveyard, and add dragoons to your hand. Once again a dragoons was sent to your GY so add a Sea Serpent into your hand, search Moulinglacia. You should have exactly 5 water monsters in your graveyard so special summon Moulinglacia and discard 2 cards out of your opponents hand. Link summon Halqi using Marincess &amp; geomancer. Activate Halqi to special summon Crystron Citree and pass turn. On opponents activation, chain with Halqi to special summon Desert Locusts and loop another card out of your opponents hand. Option to use crystron to bring out quandrax or inzektron depending on who you choose in GY.

